%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20a%20woman%2C%20and%20my%20name%20is%20Tommie%20Christopher.%20People%20have%20always%20assumed%20I%20was%20lying%20about%20my%20name.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Person%20wearing%20white%20shirt%20with%20name%20tags%20bearing%20the%20name%20Thomas%2C%20Tommie%2C%20and%20Christopher.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66675269ed9a404d829c377e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETommie%20Christopher%20Brown%20was%20bullied%20for%20her%20name%20while%20growing%20up.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Tommie%20Christopher%20Brown%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20was%20given%20a%20hand-me-down%20name%20from%20my%20dad%20and%20his%20best%20friend.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThroughout%20my%20life%2C%20people%20teased%20me%20for%20my%20name%20or%20assumed%20I%20was%20lying%20about%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAs%20an%20adult%2C%20I%20see%20my%20name%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20strength%20and%20family%20history.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBeing%20a%20girl%20with%20%26quot%3BTommie%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20first%20name%20is%20one%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20but%20having%20%26quot%3BChristopher%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20middle%20name%20turned%20quirky%20into%20confusing.%20My%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpicked-son-baby-name-unique-no-longer-trendy-angry-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ename%20is%20a%20hand-me-down%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20came%20from%20my%20dad%2C%20Thomas%2FTommy%2C%20and%20his%20late%20best%20friend%2C%20Christopher.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20what%20countless%20have%20asked%2C%20no%2C%20my%20parents%20did%20not%20expect%20nor%20want%20a%20son.%20This%20was%20going%20to%20be%20my%20name%20regardless%20of%20my%20sex%2C%20and%20as%20fate%20would%20have%20it%2C%20the%20pendulum%20swung%20in%20the%20direction%20that%20made%20my%20name%20more%20unorthodox.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20questioning%20of%20my%20honesty%20(like%20being%20told%20at%20the%20DMV%20if%20I%20wasn't%20going%20to%20%26quot%3Bcooperate%26quot%3B%20with%20them%20over%20my%20name%2C%20I%20was%20breaking%20a%20law)%2C%20my%20parents'%20sanity%2C%20even%20by%20my%20own%20family%20who%20broke%20out%20in%20disapproving%20screaming%20matches%20before%20my%20birth%2C%20and%20even%20my%20gender.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c70c5f0d-8daa-46ce-83f3-594399b24684%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20my%20name%20caused%20issues%20for%20me%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20have%20become%20more%20liberal%20with%20names%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20or%20so%20and%20no%20longer%20adhere%20so%20tightly%20to%20gendered%20expectations%20the%20way%20they%20did%20when%20I%20was%20growing%20up%20in%20the%20'90s%20and%20early%202000s.%20Having%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-male-name-fred-unusual-challenges-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ename%20that%20sounded%20so%20distinctly%20'male'%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20caused%20problems%20for%20me.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%2C%20when%20my%20mom%20and%20I%20went%20to%20get%20my%20card%20at%20the%20Social%20Security%20office%2C%20staff%20tried%20to%20force%20her%20to%20undress%20me%20to%20prove%20my%20sex%20before%20they'd%20agree%20to%20mark%20'female.'%20Now%2C%20people%20are%20realizing%20that%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20questions%20surrounding%20pronouns%20and%20gender%2C%20a%20respectful%20approach%20is%20better%20than%20one%20of%20attack%2C%20but%20I%20was%20not%20afforded%20much%20respect%20while%20growing%20up.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20goes%20without%20saying%20that%20I%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-do-if-your-child-bullying-online-at-school-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egot%20bullied%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20And%20while%20you%20might%20think%20the%20taunts%20came%20from%20the%20playground%2C%20adults%20were%20often%20the%20most%20cruel.%20I%20got%20kicked%20out%20of%20classrooms%20by%20teachers%20who%20thought%20I%20was%20pulling%20a%20fast%20one%20on%20them%20by%20insisting%20I%20was%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20myself%20during%20roll%20call.%20Some%20would%20purposefully%20call%20me%20different%20versions%20of%20my%20name%2C%20like%20%26quot%3BTammy%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BTomasina%2C%26quot%3B%20despite%20my%20pleas%20for%20them%20not%20to.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20meeting%20new%20people%2C%20I%20was%20often%20faced%20with%20intrusive%20questions%20or%20comments%20about%20my%20gender%2C%20sex%2C%20and%20whether%20or%20not%20I%20was%20simply%20%26quot%3Bconfused%26quot%3B%20about%20my%20own%20identity.%20On%20multiple%20occasions%2C%20men%20had%20told%20me%20I%20was%20%26quot%3Btoo%20pretty%20to%20think%20I%20was%20a%20boy.%26quot%3B%20An%20elementary%20school%20nurse%20once%20read%20my%20name%20and%20jokingly%20told%20me%20we%20would%20have%20to%20%26quot%3Bgo%20to%20the%20bathroom%20and%20see%20about%20that.%26quot%3B%20From%20a%20young%20age%2C%20I%20was%20forced%20to%20advocate%20for%20my%20own%20body%20and%20privacy%2C%20and%20stood%20firm%20in%20my%20refusal%20to%20allow%20adults%20to%20rewrite%20my%20identity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2265d14c56-0d18-424c-af3b-080e32108b5d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20name%20comes%20with%20family%20history%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlongside%20societal%20pushback%2C%20my%20name%20came%20with%20baggage.%20The%20best%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchanged-last-name-husband-hyphenated-maiden-married-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enames%20come%20with%20history%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20my%20history%20was%20of%20two%20rowdy%20fighters%20who%20made%20the%20streets%20and%20concert%20halls%20their%20home.%20One%20lost%20to%20gang%20violence%2C%20the%20other%20absent%20due%20to%20alcoholism%20and%20his%20own%20past%2C%20I%20had%20to%20decide%20at%20an%20extremely%20young%20age%20whether%20I%20was%20going%20to%20bring%20strength%20and%20pride%20to%20my%20name%20or%20get%20dragged%20down%20by%20it.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20Johnny%20Cash's%20%26quot%3BA%20Boy%20Named%20Sue%26quot%3B%20predicted%2C%20the%20world%20wasn't%20going%20to%20give%20me%20many%20other%20options%20aside%20from%20either%20crumbling%20beneath%20their%20rejection%20of%20both%20my%20name%20and%20namesakes%20or%20coming%20out%20swinging%20on%20the%20defense%20in%20confidence.%20Suffice%20it%20to%20say%2C%20I%20swung.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20name%20is%20the%20starting%20ground%20for%20identity.%20Through%20our%20names%2C%20we%20tell%20the%20world%20how%20to%20see%20us.%20And%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-kids-have-uncommon-names-they-like-them-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eunique%20names%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20are%20conversation%20starters%20and%20often%20storytellers%20of%20our%20past.%20I%20have%20added%20to%20the%20history%20of%20my%20familial%20name%20in%20a%20way%20I%20am%20proud%20of%2C%20changing%20the%20legacy%20of%20the%20men%20who%20came%20before%20me.%20And%20while%20my%20flight%20tickets%20often%20get%20changed%20to%20%26quot%3BMr.%20Brown%26quot%3B%20(leaving%20me%20in%20a%20frenzy%20in%20an%20airport%20in%20France)%2C%20and%20pharmacists%20accuse%20me%20of%20picking%20up%20someone%20else's%20prescriptions%2C%20there%20is%20no%20other%20name%20that%20could%20fit%20who%20I%20am%20or%20where%20I%20came%20from.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20am%20grateful%20to%20my%20parents%20for%20not%20only%20giving%20me%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20challenge%20social%20constructs%20and%20everyone%20I%20encounter.%20Thanks%20to%20them%2C%20my%20favorite%20part%20of%20any%20day%20is%20introducing%20myself.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-male-name-tommie-christopher-gender-challenges-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718095861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66675381e0790490181781b8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-male-name-tommie-christopher-gender-challenges-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I'm%20a%20woman%2C%20and%20my%20name%20is%20Tommie%20Christopher.%20I%20was%20named%20after%20my%20dad%20and%20his%20best%20friend.%20People%20have%20bullied%20me%2C%20but%20I%20love%20my%20name%20now.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Tommie%20Brown)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-male-name-tommie-christopher-gender-challenges-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NEET-UG%202024%3A%20SC%20refuses%20to%20stay%20counselling%20process%20amid%20'grace%20marks'%20row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718095527000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-01%2F08%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1704684478-7284.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-ug-2024-sc-refuses-to-stay-counselling-process-amid-grace-marks-row-124061100404_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22NEET-UG%202024%20row%3A%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20on%20pleas%20seeking%20fresh%20NEET-UG%202024%20examination%20amid%20allegations%20of%20paper%20leak%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-ug-20