the%20Chief%20Minister's%20residence%20since%20he%20took%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patnaik%2C%20after%20being%20sworn%20in%20as%20chief%20minister%20in%202000%2C%20opted%20to%20work%20from%20his%20own%20residence%20rather%20than%20moving%20into%20a%20government-allocated%20house.%20This%20decision%20set%20a%20unique%20precedent%20in%20the%20state's%20political%20history.%20For%20nearly%20a%20quarter-century%2C%20all%20official%20and%20administrative%20work%20was%20conducted%20from%20Naveen%20Niwas%20-%20a%20house%20built%20by%20his%20father%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20Biju%20Patnaik.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20BJP's%20impending%20announcement%20of%20a%20new%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20the%20state's%20administration%20has%20intensified%20its%20efforts%20to%20locate%20a%20suitable%20official%20residence.%20A%20senior%20government%20official%20stated%20that%20several%20vacant%20quarters%2C%20including%20the%20current%20Chief%20Minister's%20Grievance%20Cell%2C%20have%20been%20shortlisted%20for%20consideration.%20However%2C%20the%20transition%20will%20not%20be%20immediate.%20Once%20a%20quarter%20is%20selected%2C%20it%20will%20undergo%20necessary%20renovations%20and%20installation%20of%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interim%2C%20the%20state%20administration%20is%20planning%20to%20prepare%20a%20suite%20in%20the%20State%20Guest%20House%20to%20temporarily%20accommodate%20the%20new%20Chief%20Minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20former%20Congress%20Chief%20Ministers%20Janaki%20Ballabh%20Patnaik%20and%20Giridhar%20Gamang%20resided%20in%20a%20government%20quarter%20in%20Bhubaneswar.%20This%20house%2C%20which%20is%20now%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20Grievance%20Cell%2C%20was%20the%20official%20residence%20during%20their%20tenures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Patnaik%20family's%20original%20bungalow%20is%20in%20Cuttack%20where%20the%20three%20children%20of%20Biju%20Patnaik%20-%20Prem%2C%20Gita%20and%20Naveen%20-%20were%20born.%20For%20the%20last%20five%20decades%2C%20the%20bungalow%20has%20been%20managed%20by%20a%20caretaker.%20This%20arrangement%20began%20when%20the%20Biju%20Patnaik%20moved%20to%20Bhubaneswar%20after%20building%20Naveen%20Niwas%20in%20the%20new%20capital.%20Biju%20Patnaik%20also%20owns%20a%20house%20on%20Aurangzeb%20Road%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20which%20remains%20in%20the%20family's%20possession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20state%20elections%20in%20Odisha%20saw%20the%20end%20of%20Mr%20Patnaik's%2024-year%20rule%2C%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20storming%20to%20power%20by%20securing%2078%20seats%20in%20the%20147-member%20assembly%2C%20a%20significant%20shift%20from%20BJD's%20previous%20dominance.%20The%20BJD%20managed%20to%20secure%2051%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20took%2014%20seats%2C%20and%20three%20went%20to%20Independent%20candidates.%20In%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20BJD%20suffered%20a%20rout%20with%20the%20BJP%20winning%2020%20and%20the%20Congress%20emerging%20victorious%20in%201%20out%20of%2021%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20BJP%20government%20will%20be%20sworn%20in%20on%20tomorrow%20at%205%20pm.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20scheduled%20to%20arrive%20in%20Bhubaneswar%20at%202%3A30%20pm%20and%20proceed%20to%20Raj%20Bhavan%20from%20the%20airport.%20He%20will%20later%20attend%20the%20oath-taking%20ceremony%20at%20Janata%20Maidan%20at%205%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718093100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-01%2Fbs8mf5nc_naveen-patnaik-pti_625x300_08_January_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnaveen-patnaik-odisha-chief-minister-in-odisha-search-on-for-new-chief-ministers-official-residence-5865420%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20his%2024-year%20tenure%20as%20the%20head%20of%20the%20state's%20government%2C%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20operated%20from%20his%20personal%20home%2C%20Naveen%20Niwas%2C%20which%