bsessive%20work%20culture%20and%20stop%20with%20the%20waiting%20for%20the%20weekends%20and%20crib%20about%20Mondays%20memes.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fil101e38_ranaut-story_625x300_11_June_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BThat's%20all%20western%20brainwashing%20we%20are%20not%20a%20developed%20nation%20yet%20we%20can't%20afford%20to%20be%20bored%20and%20lazy%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20as%20many%20industry%20leaders%20have%20been%20voicing%20their%20opinions%20on%20work%20culture%20and%20how%20the%20youth%20of%20the%20country%20should%20work%20for%20long%20hours%20to%20compete%20effectively%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%20Infosys%20founder%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnarayana-murthy-suggests-70-hour-work-week-to-youngsters-sparks-debate-4516739%5C%22%3ENR%20Narayana%20Murthy's%20comments%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20ignited%20a%20social%20media%20storm%20after%20he%20remarked%20that%20people%20should%20work%2070%20hours%20a%20week%20to%20boost%20the%20country's%20overall%20work%20productivity%20and%20economy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Murthy%20drew%20parallels%20to%20Japan%20and%20Germany%2C%20countries%20that%20implemented%20the%20extended%20working%20hours.%20%26quot%3BIndia's%20work%20productivity%20is%20one%20of%20the%20lowest%20in%20the%20world.%20Unless%20we%20improve%20our%20work%20productivity%2C%20unless%20we%20reduce%20corruption%20in%20the%20government%20at%20some%20level%2C%20because%20we%20have%20been%20reading%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20the%20truth%20of%20it%2C%20unless%20we%20reduce%20the%20delays%20in%20our%20bureaucracy%20in%20taking%20this%20decision%2C%20we%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20compete%20with%20those%20countries%20that%20have%20made%20tremendous%20progress%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Infosys%20founder%20said%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20this%2C%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Asset%20Management%20Company's%20Managing%20Director%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-we-work-hard-kotaks-nilesh-shah-proposes-84-hour-work-week-internet-reacts-5821021%5C%22%3E%20Nilesh%20Shah%20added%20to%20the%20workweek%20debate%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20said%20that%20for%20India%20to%20grow%20more%20rapidly%2C%20a%20generation%20of%20people%20needs%20to%20embrace%20the%2012-hour%20workday%20culture%20which%20is%20common%20in%20China%2C%20Korea%2C%20and%20Japan.%20Mr%20Shah%20mentioned%20that%20the%2084-hour%20work%20week%20would%20%26quot%3Baccelerate%20the%20country's%20growth%26quot%3B%20and%20would%20help%20people%20to%20transfer%20to%20%26quot%3Bmiddle%20and%20upper-income%20levels%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BRecently%20in%20India%2C%20Narayana%20Murthy%20mentioned%20working%2070%20hours%20a%20week%2C%20which%20created%20a%20controversy.%20He%20said%20that%20Indians%20need%20to%20work%20like%20Koreans%2C%20Chinese%2C%20and%20Japanese.%20If%20we%20work%20hard%2C%20there%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20India's%20growth%20will%20continue%2C%20the%20pace%20will%20accelerate%2C%20and%20there%20will%20come%20a%20time%20when%20there%20will%20be%20no%20sub-Saharan%20Africa-level%20poverty%20in%20India.%20We%20will%20have%20transferred%20everyone%20to%20middle-income%20and%20upper-income%20levels.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20made%20her%20political%20debut%20as%20the%20BJP%20candidate%20from%20Himachal%20Pradesh's%20Mandi%20for%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20She%20won%20her%20first-ever%20election%20after%20defeating%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%2C%20the%20son%20of%20six-time%20chief%20minister%20Virbhadra%20Singh%20and%20state%20Congress%20chief%20Pratibha%20Sin