%22'Full%20circle'%3A%20Why%20Scindia%20said%20this%20after%20taking%20charge%20as%20telecom%20min%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718091692000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110897604%2Cimgsize-766463.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Ffull-circle-why-jyotiraditya-scindia-said-this-after-taking-charge-as-telecom-minister%2Farticleshow%2F110897039.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2053-year-old%20son%20of%20the%20late%20Congress%20leader%20Madhavrao%20Scindia%20has%20a%20significant%20history%20in%20Indian%20politics%2C%20having%20served%20as%20the%20civil%20aviation%20minister%20in%20the%20previous%20Modi%20cabinet%20since%202021.%20His%20new%20role%20marks%20a%20return%20to%20a%20familiar%20department%2C%20as%20Scindia%20previously%20served%20as%20the%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20communications%20under%20the%20UPA%20government%20from%202007%20to%202009.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Ffull-circle-why-jyotiraditya-scindia-said-this-after-taking-charge-as-telecom-minister%2Farticleshow%2F110897039.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chirag%20Paswan%20Steps%20Into%20Father's%20Shoes%2C%20Shares%20Vision%20For%20His%20Ministry%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(Ram%20Vilas)%20chief%20Chirag%20Paswan%2C%20who%20is%20among%20the%20youngest%20faces%20in%20the%20latest%20Modi%20cabinet%20or%20Modi%203.0%2C%20has%20shared%20a%20roadmap%20for%20the%20food%20processing%20ministry%20assigned%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20future%20belongs%20to%20the%20food%20processing%20sector%20and%20will%20help%20increase%20farmers'%20income%2C%20he%20told%20reporters%20after%20assuming%20charge%20this%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20his%20commitment%20to%20the%20new%20role%20entrusted%20to%20him%2C%20the%2041-year-old%20cabinet%20minister%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20wants%20to%20take%20the%20department%20to%20new%20heights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20see%20the%20involvement%20of%20food%20processing%20globally%2C%20India's%20involvement%20is%20comparatively%20very%20less%20than%20global%20involvement%20in%20the%20food%20processing%20industry.%20In%20the%20coming%20times%2C%20there%20is%20unlimited%20scope%20in%20this%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Paswan%2C%20emphasising%20the%20potential%20in%20India's%20food%20processing%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20shared%20his%20vision%20for%20the%20department%20that%20was%20helmed%20by%20his%20father%2C%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%2C%20until%20his%20death%20in%202020.%20His%20uncle%2C%20Pashupati%20Paras%2C%20headed%20it%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20own%20vision%20is%20focused%20on%20establishing%20more%20processing%20units%20so%20that%20farmers%20can%20get%20an%20appropriate%20amount%20for%20their%20produce%20and%20their%20income%20increases%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Paswan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20food%20processing%20sector%20in%20foreign%20countries%20are%20more%20advanced%2C%20said%20the%20newly%20appointed%20minister%20and%20hoped%20to%20achieve%20similar%20progress%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20foreign%20countries%2C%20several%20works%20are%20done%20through%20processing%20units%20only%2C%20whereas%20we%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20achieve%20it%20yet.%20So%2C%20I%20hope%2C%20just%20like%20my%20father%2C%20the%20late%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%2C%20I%20will%20contribute%20100%20per%20cent%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20PM%20Modi%20has%20assured%20him%20of%20support%20in%20elevating%20the%20department's%20status.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20met%20him%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20assured%20me%20that%20in%20the%20future%2C%20we%20will%20take%20th