affected...%20so%20we%20need%20answers.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20though%2C%20said%20counselling%20for%20admissions%20will%20continue.%20Justices%20Vikram%20Nath%20and%20Ahsanuddin%20Amanullah%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20stopping%20counselling%26quot%3B.%20The%20matter%20was%20then%20posted%20to%20July%208%20and%20will%20be%20heard%20with%20a%20plea%20filed%20before%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20hearing%20a%20fresh%20petition%20in%20the%20ongoing%20row%20over%20the%20NEET-UG%202024%20results%20that%20claim%20discrepancies%20in%20scores%20and%20alleged%20preferential%20treatment%20to%20some%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20asked%20for%20the%20scores%20from%20the%20May%205%20exam%20to%20be%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20also%20asked%20for%20a%20fresh%20exam%20to%20be%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20-%20from%20Telangana%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20-%20have%20claimed%20variances%20in%20grant%20of%20grace%20marks%2C%20for%20which%20they%20say%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bno%20defined%20logic%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20drawn%20the%20court's%20attention%20to%20%26quot%3Bstatistically%20impossible%26quot%3B%20marks%2C%20including%20students%20scoring%20the%20maximum%20-%20720%20of%20720.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20has%20no%20defined%20logic%20for%20grace%20marks%20given%20(and)%20no%20list%20has%20been%20shared%20as%20per%20given%20grace%20marks.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20reason%20for%20awarding%20grace%20marks%20is%20'wastage%20of%20time'...%20but%20this%20was%20never%20disclosed%20in%20information%20bulletin%20before%20the%20exam%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20petitioners%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20have%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20fact%2067%20students%20from%20one%20particular%20coaching%20centre%20got%20a%20full%20720%20marks%2C%20and%20also%20that%20a%20provisional%20answer%20key%20released%20by%20the%20NTA%20had%20been%20contested%20by%20over%2013%2C000%20students%20as%20the%20problem%20pointed%20to%20a%20different%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderscoring%20the%20dangers%20of%20cheating%20in%20a%20medical%20test%2C%20the%20plea%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20field%20requires%20a%20deep%20understanding%20of%20scientific%20and%20medical%20knowledge...%20cheating%20or%20using%20unfair%20means%20to%20pass%20an%20exam%20can%20lead%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20competence%20and%20endanger%20lives%20of%20patients.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20also%20noted%20that%20cheating%20in%20exams%20%26quot%3Bundermines%20the%20principles%20of%20meritocracy%20and%20equal%20opportunities%2C%20which%20are%20essential%20for%20social%20mobility%20and%20fairness%20in%20society%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20perpetuates%20inequalities%20by%20favoring%20those%20who%20can%20afford%20to%20pay%20for%20leaked%20exam%20papers%20or%20engage%20in%20fraudulent%20activities%2C%20while%20disadvantaging%20those%20who%20rely%20on%20their%20hard%20work%20and%20merit%20to%20succeed%20and%20the%20same%20also%20impacts%20the%20society%20as%20a%20whole%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20plea%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2017%2C%20while%20the%20bench%20led%20by%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20was%20hearing%20a%20similar%20plea%2C%20the%20court%20issued%20a%20notice%20but%20did%20not%20halt%20declaration%20of%20results.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20NTA%20has%20decided%20a%20high-powered%20committee%20will%20analyse%20the%20grievances%20of%201%2C600%20students%20who%20have%20already%20appeared%20for%20the%20NEET%202024%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718091540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F9ijrm348_supreme-court_625x300_15_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-ug-2024-exam-paper-leak-supreme-court-sanctity-of-exam-affected-need-answers-supreme-court-on-neet-ug-row-5865003%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Sup