reate%20original%20images%20and%20retrieve%20the%20most%20relevant%20data%20when%20users%20need%20it.%20The%20push%20also%20includes%20a%20revamped%20version%20of%20Siri%2C%20the%20company's%20once-pioneering%20digital%20assistant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20is%20making%20a%20high-stakes%20bid%20to%20catch%20up%20with%20rivals%20in%20the%20booming%20AI%20market.%20After%20falling%20behind%20tech%20peers%20like%20Alphabet%20Inc.'s%20Google%20and%20Microsoft%20Corp.%2C%20the%20company%20is%20counting%20on%20a%20streamlined%20interface%20-%20and%20loyal%20customer%20base%20-%20to%20regain%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20moment%20we've%20been%20working%20toward%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Senior%20Vice%20President%20Craig%20Federighi%2C%20who%20oversees%20software%20engineering%2C%20said%20at%20the%20event.%20He%20described%20Apple%20Intelligence%20as%20%26quot%3BAI%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20alluding%20to%20an%20old%20slogan%20about%20the%20Mac%20computer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20partnership%20with%20OpenAI%2C%20which%20Bloomberg%20reported%20on%20before%20the%20event%2C%20will%20let%20customers%20access%20ChatGPT%20via%20Siri%20at%20no%20extra%20cost.%20Apple%20Intelligence%20will%20begin%20rolling%20out%20later%20this%20year%2C%20but%20some%20features%20-%20including%20the%20ability%20for%20Siri%20to%20precisely%20control%20features%20within%20apps%20-%20won't%20come%20until%20next%20year.%20Support%20for%20languages%20beyond%20English%20also%20won't%20arrive%20until%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20Sam%20Altman%20was%20at%20Monday's%20event%20and%20wrote%20on%20the%20social%20media%20site%20X%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20happy%26quot%3B%20to%20be%20teaming%20up%20with%20Apple.%20While%20the%20ChatGPT%20integration%20will%20be%20free%2C%20paid%20subscribers%20to%20OpenAI%20will%20get%20additional%20features%20over%20time.%20Apple%2C%20which%20has%20also%20held%20talks%20with%20Google%20about%20using%20that%20company's%20Gemini%20feature%2C%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20support%20other%20services%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnsuring%20that%20customer%20data%20is%20secure%20was%20a%20major%20theme%20of%20the%20presentation.%20A%20system%20called%20Private%20Cloud%20Compute%20will%20help%20keep%20users'%20information%20safe%20when%20it's%20being%20sent%20to%20data%20centers%2C%20Federighi%20said.%20Apple%20Intelligence%20will%20also%20support%20AI-created%20emoji%20called%20Genmoji%20and%20automated%20photo%20editing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple's%20iOS%2018%20and%20iPadOS%20-%20its%20iPhone%20and%20iPad%20software%20-%20will%20get%20features%20that%20improve%20customization%2C%20productivity%20and%20communication.%20Some%20additions%20will%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAn%20upgraded%20home%20screen%20will%20let%20users%20place%20icons%20anywhere.%20App%20icon%20colors%20can%20also%20be%20changed%2C%20and%20they%20can%20be%20tinted%20when%20the%20device%20is%20placed%20in%20dark%20mode.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20new%20Control%20Center%20includes%20support%20for%20third-party%20controls%2C%20multiple%20pages%20of%20settings%20and%20an%20updated%20look.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20iPhone%2014%20and%20more%20recent%20models%20will%20get%20support%20for%20text%20messaging%20via%20satellites.%20That%20was%20previously%20available%20in%20emergency%20situations.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Messages%20app%20will%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20schedule%20a%20text%20to%20be%20sent%20later.%20The%20Tapbacks%20feature%2C%20which%20lets%20users%20quickly%20respond%20to%20texts%20with%20things%20like%20a%20heart%20or%20question%20mark%2C%20will%20now%20work%20with%20an%20emoji%20or%20digital%20sticker.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECustomers%20can%20set%20up%20effects%20-%20such%20as%20a%20shaking%20word%20-%20for%20individual%20words%20and%20phrases%2C%20rather%20than%20entire%20texts.%20And%20there's%20rich%20text%20support%2C%20which%20will%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20Apple%20customers%20to%20communicate%20with%20Android%20users.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20Passwords%20app%20will%20manage%20secure%20logins%2C%20passkeys%20and%20Wi-Fi%20account%20details.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20redesigned%20Photos%20app%20will%20use%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20improve%20editing.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere's%20the%20ability%20to%20lock%20any%20app%20behind%20Face%20ID.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20iPad%20gets%20the%20Calculator%20app%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20and%20it%20will%20let%20people%20solve%20handwritten%20math%20equations%20using%20an%20Apple%20Pencil.%20That%20app's%20absence%20from%20the%20iPad%20was%20a%20longstanding%20issue%20among%20customers%2C%20and%20the%20new%20feature%20was%20announced%20to%20applause%20at%20Monday's%20event.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestors%20gave%20a%20tepid%20reaction%20to%20the%20event%20-%20a%20not-uncommon%20reaction%20when%20Apple%20debuts%20long-anticipated%20new%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shares%20fell%20almost%202%25%20to%20%24193.12%20in%20New%20York%2C%20leaving%20the%20stock%20little%20changed%20for%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Cupertino%2C%20California-based%20company%20also%20rolled%20out%20macOS%20Sequoia%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20same%20Apple%20Intelligence%20features%20as%20the%20iPad%20and%20iPhone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20its%20other%20enhancements%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20ability%20to%20receive%20and%20interact%20with%20iPhone%20notifications.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20ability%20to%20drag%20and%20drop%20files%20between%20devices.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMirroring%20an%20iPhone's%20display%20so%20it%20can%20be%20used%20on%20a%20Mac's%20screen.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20ability%20to%20organize%20Mac%20application%20windows%20as%20tiles%20that%20stick%20to%20different%20portions%20of%20the%20display.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAnd%20the%20company%20unveiled%20visionOS%202%2C%20the%20latest%20version%20of%20its%20software%20for%20the%20Vision%20Pro%20headset.%20That%20has%20new%20features%20for%20photos%20and%20handling%20office%20work%2C%20including%3A%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20ability%20to%20turn%20regular%20photos%20into%203D%20spatial%20pictures.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENew%20hand%20gestures%20for%20opening%20the%20Home%20View%20and%20Control%20Center.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20new%20version%20of%20the%20Mac%20Virtual%20Display%20feature%20that%20can%20create%20a%20virtual%20wraparound%20screen.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20ability%20to%20AirPlay%20content%20from%20an%20iPhone%2C%20iPad%20or%20Mac%20into%20the%20Vision%20Pro.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20also%20announced%20plans%20to%20launch%20the%20Vision%20Pro%20internationally%2C%20with%20preorders%20beginning%20in%20China%2C%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20Japan%20and%20Singapore%20on%20June%2013.%20The%20device%20will%20go%20on%20sale%20in%20those%20areas%20June%2028.%20That%20will%20be%20followed%20by%20Australia%2C%20Canada%2C%20France%2C%20Germany%20and%20the%20UK.%20Preorders%20will%20begin%20in%20those%20countries%20June%2028%2C%20and%20sales%20will%20start%20July%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20AirPods%20software%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20will%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20hear%20users'%20voices%20during%20a%20phone%20call%20by%20removing%20background%20noise.%20The%20Apple%20Watch%20will%20get%20additional%20health%20capabilities%2C%20such%20as%20enhanced%20pregnancy%20tracking%20and%20an%20app%20that%20shows%20at-a-glance%20vital%20statistics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20AI%20features%20were%20the%20biggest%20focus%20of%20the%20event.%20Those%20tools%20will%20also%20include%20the%20ability%20to%20transcribe%20phone%20calls%20and%20voice%20memos%2C%20solve%20advanced%20math%20equations%2C%20sort%20through%20email%2C%20and%20prioritize%20notifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Apple%20had%20an%20early%20lead%20in%20AI%20after%20it%20launched%20Siri%20in%202011%2C%20its%20technology%20was%20quickly%20overtaken%20by%20the%20Google%20Assistant%20and%20Amazon.com%20Inc.'s%20Alexa.%20Then%20AI%20took%20another%20giant%20leap%20forward%20when%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%20arrived%20at%20the%20end%20of%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20led%20to%20a%20flurry%20of%20other%20services%2C%20including%20ones%20from%20Google%2C%20Microsoft%20and%20Meta%20Platforms%20Inc.%20Samsung%20Electronics%20Co.%20-%20Apple's%20biggest%20smartphone%20rival%20-%20also%20integrated%20Google%20AI%20features%20into%20its%20devices%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20CEO%20Tim%20Cook%20is%20now%20under%20pressure%20to%20show%20that%20the%20iPhone%20maker%20can%20lead%20again.%20The%20company%20also%20is%20contending%20with%20a%20broader%20sales%20slump.%20Revenue%20declined%20in%20five%20of%20the%20past%20six%20quarters%20in%20the%20face%20of%20sluggish%20smartphone%20demand%20and%20a%20slowdown%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Cook%20said%20AI%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bthe%20next%20big%20step%20for%20Apple.%26quot%3B%20Though%20the%20company%20won't%20make%20money%20directly%20on%20the%20new%20features%2C%20the%20hope%20is%20to%20make%20users%20more%20loyal%20and%20prod%20them%20to%20upgrade%20more%20frequently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20think%20Apple%20Intelligence%20is%20going%20to%20be%20indispensable%20to%20the%20products%20that%20already%20play%20such%20an%20integral%20role%20in%20our%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718085480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fv5sbfnhg_apple-generic_625x300_11_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fapple-intelligence-wdc-event-2024-all-about-apples-new-ai-for-the-rest-of-us-features-5864531%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apple