C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-03%2F31%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1711904104-2731.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Findigo-shares-fall-over-4-after-11-mn-shares-change-hands-via-block-deal-124061100220_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22IndiGo%20block%20deal%3A%20Reports%20suggest%20Rahul%20Bhatia-led%20InterGlobe%20Enterprises%20was%20the%20likely%20seller%20of%20its%202%20per%20cent%20stake%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Findigo-shares-fall-over-4-after-11-mn-shares-change-hands-via-block-deal-124061100220_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Findigo-shares-fall-over-4-after-11-mn-shares-change-hands-via-block-deal-124061100220_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Findigo-shares-fall-over-4-after-11-mn-shares-change-hands-via-block-deal-124061100220_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Asked%20About%20Maldivian%20Probe%20Into%20Deals%20With%20India%2C%20S%20Jaishankar%20Says%20This%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ES%20Jaishankar%20officially%20assumed%20office%20as%20India's%20Foreign%20Minister%20today.%20Mr%20Jaishankar%2C%2069%2C%20was%20among%20several%20senior%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20including%20Rajnath%20Singh%2C%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20Nitin%20Gadkari%2C%20and%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%2C%20who%20retained%20their%20respective%20ministries%20from%20the%20previous%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscussing%20India's%20relationship%20with%20Pakistan%20and%20China%20for%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20the%20two%20countries%20pose%20different%20challenges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20any%20country%20and%20especially%20in%20a%20democracy%2C%20it%20is%20a%20very%20big%20deal%20for%20a%20government%20to%20get%20elected%20three%20times%20in%20a%20row.%20So%20the%20world%20will%20definitely%20feel%20that%20today%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20political%20stability%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20noted.%20%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20Pakistan%20and%20China%20are%20concerned%2C%20the%20relations%20with%20those%20countries%20are%20different%2C%20and%20the%20problems%20there%20are%20also%20different.%20Our%20focus%20with%20regard%20to%20China%20will%20be%20on%20finding%20a%20solution%20for%20the%20border%20issues%20and%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20we%20would%20want%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20issue%20of%20years-old%20cross-border%20terrorism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20assumed%20office%20in%20Delhi%20after%20a%20grand%20swearing-in%20ceremony%2C%20where%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20took%20the%20oath%20of%20office%20along%20with%2071%20ministers%20of%20the%20new%20coalition%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20questioned%20about%20the%20Maldivian%20parliamentary%20probe%20on%20previous%20agreements%20with%20India%2C%20Jaishankar%20responded%20diplomatically%2C%20reflecting%20his%20seasoned%20approach%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20a%20meeting%20with%20President%20Muizzu%20and%20even%20PM%20Modi%20met%20him.%20I%20even%20had%20the%20honour%20to%20call%20on%20him.%20So%20I%20will%20prefer%20to%20be%20guided%20by%20my%20experience%20and%20conversation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETies%20between%20India%20and%20the%20Maldives%20came%20under%20severe%20strain%20since%20President%20Muizzu%2C%20known%20for%20his%20pro-China%20stance%2C%20took%20charge%20of%20the%20top%20office.%20Within%20hours%20of%20his%20oath%2C%20he%20had%20demanded%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20from%20Maldives.%20The%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20were%20replaced%20by%20civilians%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20India's%20ambitions%20for%20a%20permanent%20seat%20on%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%20(UNSC)%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20India's%20position%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bfriend%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20Modi%20government's%20foreign%20policy%20will%20take%20the%20country%20to%20greater%20heights.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20different%20aspects%20and%20I%20am%20fully%20confident%20that%20under%20PM%20Modi's%20leadership%2C%20the%20foreign%20policy%20of%20Modi%203.0%20will%20be%20very%20successful.%20For%20us%2C%20the%20influence%20of%20India%20has%20been%20steadily%20growing%2C%20not%20just%20in%20terms%20of%20our%20own%20perception%20but%20also%20what%20the%20other%20countries%20think.%20They%20feel%20that%20India%20is%20truly%20their%20friend%20and%20they%20have%20seen%20that%20in%20times%20of%20crisis%2C%20if%20there%20is%20one%20country%20that%20stands%20with%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20it%20is%20India.%20They%20have%20seen%20that%20when%20we%20put%20forward%20the%20African%20Union%20membership%20during%20the%20presidency%20of%20G20%2C%20the%20world%20trusted%20us%20and%20our%20responsibilities%20are%20also%20increasing%2C%20so%20we%20also%20believe%20that%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20PM%20Modi%2C%20India's%20identity%20in%20the%20world%20will%20definitely%20increase%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20has%20served%20as%20India's%20Foreign%20Secretary%20under%20the%20first%20Modi%20government%20(2015-18)%20and%20held%20ambassadorial%20roles%20in%20the%20United%20States%20(2013-15)%2C%20China%20(2009-2013)%2C%20and%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20(2000-2004).%20Additionally%2C%20he%20was%20India's%20High%20Commissioner%20to%20Singapore%20(2007-2009)%20and%20has%20had%20assignments%20in%20embassies%20in%20Moscow%2C%20Colombo%2C%20Budapest%2C%20and%20Tokyo%2C%20along%20with%20roles%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20and%20the%20President's%20Secretariat.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%