a.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fanupam-kher-showers-love-on-rajinikanth-calls-him-gods-gift-to-mankind-video-inside%2Farticleshow%2F110892036.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110892036.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERajinikanth%20graced%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%20Prime%20Minister.%20Speaking%20to%20reporters%20at%20the%20airport%20before%20departing%20for%20Delhi%2C%20he%20acknowledged%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20event%2C%20stating%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20going%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20swearing-in%20ceremony...%20It%20is%20a%20very%20historic%20event%E2%80%A6%20Assuming%20office%20for%20the%20third%20consecutive%20term%20is%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20big%20achievement%2C%20my%20hearty%20greetings%20to%20him.%20People%20have%20elected%20a%20robust%20opposition%20which%20is%20a%20healthy%20sign%20for%20democracy.%E2%80%9D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fanupam-kher-showers-love-on-rajinikanth-calls-him-gods-gift-to-mankind-video-inside%2Farticleshow%2F110892036.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Modi%203.0%20Ministers%20Sign%20In%2C%20BJP%20Has%20Two%20More%20Key%20Posts%20To%20Fill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20Modi%203.0's%20swearing-in%20done%20and%20portfolios%20allocated%20to%20the%20new%20ministers%2C%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20now%20has%20two%20key%20tasks%20at%20hand%20--%20choosing%20a%20new%20Speaker%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20naming%20a%20party%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20president%20JP%20Nadda%2C%20who%20was%20Health%20Minister%20in%20the%20first%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20has%20been%20brought%20back%20to%20the%20cabinet%20this%20time.%20He%20now%20holds%20the%20portfolios%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Chemicals%20and%20Fertilizers.%20The%20new%20BJP%20president%20will%20have%20to%20hit%20the%20ground%20running%20as%20Assembly%20elections%20are%20due%20later%20this%20year%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Jharkhand%20and%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20task%20on%20the%20BJP's%20agenda%20is%20finalising%20the%20NDA's%20choice%20for%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker.%20N%20Chandrababu%20Naidu's%20TDP%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20JDU%2C%20BJP's%20key%20allies%20whose%20support%20is%20critical%20for%20the%20government's%20majority%2C%20are%20eyeing%20the%20post%2C%20it%20is%20learnt.%20This%20comes%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20mutinies%20over%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20years%20that%20have%20split%20parties%20and%20toppled%20governments.%20In%20such%20cases%2C%20the%20anti-defection%20law%20comes%20into%20play%2C%20and%20the%20Speaker%20of%20the%20House%20becomes%20a%20crucial%20post.%20Mr%20Naidu%20and%20Mr%20Kumar%2C%20both%20Coalition-era%20veterans%2C%20want%20the%20Speaker's%20post%20as%20a%20shield%20against%20any%20such%20tactic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20in%20the%20BJP%2C%20however%2C%20have%20said%20they%20are%20not%20keen%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20Speaker's%20post.%20While%20there%20is%20no%20official%20word%20yet%2C%20the%20name%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20BJP%20chief%20D%20Purandeshwari%20is%20doing%20the%20rounds%20for%20the%20key%20position.%20Ms%20Purandeshwari%20is%20the%20daughter%20of%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20legendary%20actor%20NT%20Rama%20Rao%20and%20the%20sister-in-law%20of%20Mr%20Naidu.%20Her%20husband%2C%20Daggubati%20Venkateshwara%20Rao%2C%20is%20a%20former%20Congress%20MP%20and%20MLA%20who%20later%20joined%20YSR%20Congress%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20first%20elected%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20a%20Congress%20ticket%20and%20also%20served%20as%20a%20Union%20Minister%20in%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government.%20She%20resigned%20from%20the%20Congress%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20UPA%20government's%20decision%20to%20carve%20the%20state%20of%20Telangana%20out%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20Ms%20Purandeshwari%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%202014%20and%20has%20risen%20to%20become%20its%20state%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-time%20MP%20not%20being%20accommodated%20in%20the%20Modi%203.0%20cabinet%20has%20surprised%20many%20and%20set%20off%20speculation%20that%20she%20may%20be%20the%20BJP's%20choice%20for%20the%20Speaker%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20post%20that%20remained%20vacant%20through%20Modi%202.0%20is%20that%20of%20the%20Deputy%20Speaker%20of%20Lok%20Sabha.%20During%20the%20first%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20M%20Thambidurai%20of%20the%20AIADMK%2C%20then%20an%20ally%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20was%20named%20for%20the%20post.%20The%20question%20is%20if%20the%20BJP%20will%20keep%20this%20post%20or%20offer%20it%20to%20its%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718081580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fnhb2dr6_modi-30_625x300_11_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmodi-3-0-lok-sabha-speaker-bjp-president-as-modi-3-0-ministers-sign-in-bjp-has-two-more-key-posts-to-fill-5864056%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20Modi%203.0's%20swearing-in%20done%20and%20portfolios%20allocated%20to%20the%20new%20ministers%2C%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20now%20has%20two%20key%20tasks%20at%20hand%20--%20choosing%20a%20new%20Speaker%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20naming%20a%20party%20chief.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmodi-3-0-lok-sabha-speaker-bjp-president-as-modi-3-0-ministers-sign-in-bjp-has-two-more-key-posts-to-fill-5864056%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmodi-3-0-lok-sabha-speaker-bjp-president-as-modi-3-0-