0organizations%20said%20in%20a%20joint%20statement%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20just%20another%20example%20of%20our%20two-tiered%20system%20of%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20statement%2C%20issued%20by%20The%20Legal%20Aid%20Society%2C%20The%20Bronx%20Defenders%2C%20New%20York%20County%20Defender%20Services%2C%20and%20Neighborhood%20Defender%20Service%20of%20Harlem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20is%20not%20getting%20preferential%20treatment%20by%20being%20allowed%20to%20do%20his%20interview%20via%20video%20and%20with%20his%20lawyer%2C%20a%20city%20spokeswoman%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20common%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20not%20unusual%2C%20and%20it's%20been%20an%20option%20from%20even%20before%20COVID%2C%26quot%3B%20Ivette%20Davila-Richards%2C%20a%20deputy%20press%20secretary%20for%20the%20mayor's%20office%2C%20said%20of%20Trump's%20virtual%20interview.%20%26quot%3BNo%20exceptions%20are%20being%20made%20because%20it's%20President%20Trump%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20true%20that%20defendants%20who%20are%20locked%20up%20while%20awaiting%20sentencing%20typically%20do%20pre-sentencing%20interviews%20via%20video%2C%20defense%20lawyers%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20defendants%20like%20Trump%2C%20who%20are%20at%20liberty%2C%20are%20almost%20always%20required%20to%20appear%20alone%20and%20in%20person%20for%20their%20probation%20interviews%2C%20lawyers%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20was%20able%20to%20have%20attorney%20Todd%20Blanche%20at%20his%20side%20only%20through%20the%20most%20uncommon%20of%20circumstances%2C%20attorneys%20also%20complained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20judge%2C%20New%20York%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Manhattan%20Juan%20Merchan%2C%20on%20Friday%20ordered%20probation%20to%20allow%20Blanche%20to%20attend%20Trump's%20interview%20after%20prosecutors%20did%20not%20fight%20the%20request%2C%20court%20filings%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20never%20been