ent%20in%20my%20direction%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20concentrate%20solely%20on%20research%20and%20sought%20someone%20who%20could%20effectively%20market%20the%20product.%20Chintan%20was%20the%20perfect%20fit%20for%20this%20role%2C%20and%20our%20responsibilities%20are%20divided%20along%20similar%20lines%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitting%20across%20from%20me%2C%20holding%20a%20bottle%20that%20resembled%20a%20typical%20single-use%20plastic%20bottle%20%E2%80%94%20with%20the%20words%20%E2%80%98I%20am%20a%20bottle%20but%20I%20am%20not%20plastic%E2%80%99%20printed%20on%20it%20%E2%80%94%20Nikhil%20is%20confident%20that%20the%20bottle%20will%20decompose%20in%20nature%20within%20six%20months%20or%20180%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20tap%20the%20bottle%2C%20and%20it%20will%20sound%20like%20plastic%3B%20you%20can%20touch%20it%2C%20you%20can%20feel%20it%20%E2%80%94%20it%20looks%20identical.%20The%20only%20difference%20is%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340584%2Fkarnataka-suresh-maithili-bhoomi-agri-ventures-turns-areca-palm-leaf-into-vegan-leather%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20biodegradable%2C%20plant-based%2C%20and%20environmentally%20friendly%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20material%20and%20the%20manufacturing%20process%2C%20Nikhil%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20my%20research%2C%20I%20explored%20how%20plants%20could%20be%20utilised%20to%20create%20various%20materials.%20Just%20as%20plants%20can%20be%20used%20to%20make%20leather%2C%20I%20was%20investigating%20similar%20possibilities%20when%20I%20stumbled%20upon%20the%20remarkable%20properties%20of%20sugarcane.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2