2%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20almost%20midnight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanjit%20Singh%20was%20half-asleep%20when%20his%20wife%2C%20Jaswinder%2C%20woke%20him%20up%20and%20reminded%20him%20about%20the%20workshop%20on%20natural%20farming.%20He%20wondered%20what%20she%20was%20yapping%20about%20and%20went%20to%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20morning%20when%20Ranjit%20enquired%2C%20he%20got%20to%20know%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F55881%2Fzero-budget-natural-farming-subash-palekar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESubhash%20Palekar%20Natural%20Farming%20%3C%2Fa%3Eworkshop%20that%20could%20benefit%20the%20couple%20immensely.%20On%20her%20advice%2C%20he%20immediately%20left%20for%20Solan%2C%20150%20km%20away%20from%20his%20village%20in%20Kanshipur%2C%20Sirmaur%2C%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20training%2C%20Ranjit%E2%80%99s%20perspective%20on%20farming%20took%20a%20complete%20U-turn.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20decades%2C%20we%20had%20been%20growing%20crops%20using%20chemical%20fertilisers%20like%20urea%2C%20weedicides%2C%20and%20chemical%20insecticides.%20I%20never%20knew%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20harm%20that%20we%20were%20causing%20ourselves%20and%20to%20those%20buying%20crops%20from%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2057-year-old%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidering%20inorganic%20farming%20a%20sin%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20convert%20their%20entire%20seven-bigha%20(1.4%20acre)%20land%20into%20a%20natural%20farm.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20training%2C%20I%20thought%20of%20growing%20crops%20on%20a%20small%20part%20of%20our%20land%20using%20natural%20farming%2C%20but%20later%2C%20I%20swore%20never%20to%20use%20any%20chemical%20fertilisers%20in%20the%20field%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%